nniere_300x169_fr.jpg" class="image wp-image-230229  attachment-full size-full" alt="" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" srcset="https://www.rcinet.ca/fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/banniere_300x169_fr.jpg 300w, https://www.rcinet.ca/fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/banniere_300x169_fr-240x135.jpg 240w, https://www.rcinet.ca/fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/03/banniere_300x169_fr-205x115.jpg 205w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div><div id="sow-editor-8" class="widget-wrapper widget_sow-editor"><div class="so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base"><h4>La vie au temps de la COVID-19</h4>
